Require Import WildCat.Core WildCat.Bifunctor WildCat.Prod WildCat.Equiv.
Require Import WildCat.NatTrans WildCat.Square WildCat.Opposite.

(** * Building Symmetric Monoidal Categories *)

(** The following construction is what we call the "twist construction". It is a way to build a symmetric monoidal category from simpler pieces than the axioms ask for.

The core observation is that the associator can be broken up into a [braid] and what we call a [twist] map. The twist map takes a right associated triple [(A, (B, C))] and swaps the first two factors [(B, (A, C)]. Together with functoriality of the tensor and the braiding, here termed [braid] we can simplify the axioms we ask for.

For instance, the hexagon identity is about associators, but if we unfold the definition and simplify the diagram, we get a diagram about only twists and braids.

This means in practice, you can show a category has a symmetric monoidal structure by proving some simpler axioms. This idea has been used in TriJoin.v to show the associativity of join for example. *)

Section TwistConstruction.
  (** The aim of this section is to build a symmetric monoidal category. We do this piecewise so that the separate steps are useful in and of themselves.

  Our basic starting assumption is that we have a category with equivalences, a bifunctor called the tensor product, and a unit object.*)
  Context (A : Type) `{HasEquivs A}
    (cat_tensor : A -> A -> A) (cat_tensor_unit : A)
    `{!Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor, !Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor}

    (** Next we postulate the existence of a [braid] map. This takes a tensor pair and swaps the factors. We also postulate that [braid] is natural in both factors and self-inverse. *)
    (braid : SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor)

    (** We postulate the existence of a [twist] map. This takes a right associated triple [(A, (B, C))] and swaps the first two factors [(B, (A, C)]. We also postulate that [twist] is natural in all three factors and self-inverse. *)
    (twist : forall a b c, cat_tensor a (cat_tensor b c) $-> cat_tensor b (cat_tensor a c))
    (twist_twist : forall a b c, twist a b c $o twist b a c $== Id _)
    (twist_nat : forall a a' b b' c c' (f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b') (h : c $-> c'),
      twist a' b' c' $o fmap11 cat_tensor f (fmap11 cat_tensor g h)
      $== fmap11 cat_tensor g (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) $o twist a b c)

    (** We assume that there is a natural isomorphism [right_unitor] witnessing the right unit law. The left unit law will be derived from this one. We also assume a coherence called [twist_unitor] which determines how the right_unitor interacts with [braid] and [twist]. This is the basis of the triangle axiom. *)
    (right_unitor : RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit)
    (twist_unitor : forall a b, fmap01 cat_tensor a (right_unitor b)
      $== braid b a $o fmap01 cat_tensor b (right_unitor a) $o twist a b cat_tensor_unit)

    (** The hexagon identity is about the interaction of associators and braids. We will derive this axiom from an analogous one for twists and braids. *)
    (twist_hexagon : forall a b c,
      fmap01 cat_tensor c (braid b a) $o twist b c a $o fmap01 cat_tensor b (braid a c)
      $== twist a c b $o fmap01 cat_tensor a (braid b c) $o twist b a c)

    (** The 9-gon identity. TODO: explain this *)
    (twist_9_gon : forall a b c d,
        fmap01 cat_tensor c (braid (cat_tensor a b) d)
        $o twist (cat_tensor a b) c d
        $o braid (cat_tensor c d) (cat_tensor a b)
        $o twist a (cat_tensor c d) b
        $o fmap01 cat_tensor a (braid b (cat_tensor c d))
      $== fmap01 cat_tensor c (twist a d b)
        $o fmap01 cat_tensor c (fmap01 cat_tensor a (braid b d))
        $o twist a c (cat_tensor b d)
        $o fmap01 cat_tensor a (twist b c d))
  .

  (** *** Setup *)

  (** Before starting the proofs, we need to setup some useful definitions and helpful lemmas for working with diagrams. *)

  (** We give notations and abbreviations to the morphisms that will appear in diagrams. This helps us read the goal and understand what is happening, otherwise it is too verbose. *)
  Declare Scope monoidal_scope.
  Local Infix "‚äó" := cat_tensor (at level 40) : monoidal_scope.
  Local Infix "‚äóR" := (fmap01 cat_tensor) (at level 40) : monoidal_scope.
  Local Infix "‚äóL" := (fmap10 cat_tensor) (at level 40) : monoidal_scope.
  Local Notation "f ‚àò g" := (f $o g) (at level 61, left associativity, format "f  '/' '‚àò'  g") : monoidal_scope.
  (** TODO: in 8.19 this notation causes issues, when updating to 8.20 we should uncomment this. *)
  (* Local Notation "f $== g :> A" := (GpdHom (A := A) f g)
    (at level 70, format "'[v' '[v' f ']' '/'  $== '/'  '[v' g ']'  '/' :>  '[' A ']' ']'")
    : long_path_scope. *)
  Local Open Scope monoidal_scope.

  (** [twist] is an equivalence which we will call [twiste]. *)
  Local Definition twiste a b c
    : cat_tensor a (cat_tensor b c) $<~> cat_tensor b (cat_tensor a c)
    := cate_adjointify (twist a b c) (twist b a c)
        (twist_twist a b c) (twist_twist b a c).

  (** *** Finer naturality *)

  (** The naturality postulates we have for [twist] are natural in all their arguments simultaneously. We show the finer naturality of [twist] in each argument separately as this becomes more useful in practice. *)

  
A: Type
IsGraph0: IsGraph A
Is2Graph0: Is2Graph A
Is01Cat0: Is01Cat A
H: Is1Cat A
H0: HasEquivs A
cat_tensor: A -> A -> A
cat_tensor_unit: A
Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, a': A
f: a $-> a'
b, c: A
twist a' b c ‚àò f ‚äóL (b ‚äó c) $== b ‚äóR (f ‚äóL c)
‚àò twist a b c

    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==

  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c

a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit

‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c

twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==

‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d

c: A

‚àò twist a b c

twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, c': A
h: c $-> c'
fmap11 cat_tensor (Id b) (fmap11 cat_tensor (Id a) h) $==
b ‚äóR (a ‚äóR h)

  (** *** Movement lemmas *)

  (** Here we collect lemmas about moving morphisms around in a diagram. We could have created [cate_moveL_eM]-style lemmas for [CatIsEquiv] but this leads to a lot of unnecessary unfolding and duplication. It is typically easier to use a hand crafted lemma for each situation. *)

c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
f: d $-> a ‚äó (b ‚äó c)
g: d $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
p: twist a b c ‚àò f $== g
twiste a b c ‚àò twist b a c $-> Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))

Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
f: b ‚äó (a ‚äó c) $-> d
g: a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> d
p: f ‚àò twist a b c $== g
f ‚àò ?Goal $== g

twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d, e: A
f: e $-> a ‚äó (b ‚äó (c ‚äó d))
g: e $-> a ‚äó (c ‚äó (b ‚äó d))
p: a ‚äóR twist b c d ‚àò f $== g
twist b c d ‚àò twist c b d $-> Id (c ‚äó (b ‚äó d))

      apply twist_twist.

twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d, e: A
f: a ‚äó (c ‚äó (b ‚äó d)) $-> e
g: a ‚äó (b ‚äó (c ‚äó d)) $-> e
p: f ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d $== g
emap01 cat_tensor a (twiste b c d) $==
a ‚äóR twist b c d

twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, a', b', c': A
f: a $-> a'
g: b $-> b'
h: c $-> c'
Square (braid c (a ‚äó b)) 
  (braid c' (a' ‚äó b')) 
  ?Goal
  (fmap (uncurry cat_tensor)
     (fmap (uncurry cat_tensor) (f, g), h))

  (fmap11 cat_tensor f (fmap11 cat_tensor g h))
  (fmap11 cat_tensor h
     (fmap (uncurry cat_tensor) (f, g)))

      (** The second square is just the naturality of twist. *)

‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, a', b', c': A
f: a $-> a'
g: b $-> b'
h: c $-> c'
Square (fmap11 cat_tensor (Id a) (braid b c))
  (fmap11 cat_tensor (Id a') (braid b' c'))
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f (fmap11 cat_tensor g h))
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f (fmap11 cat_tensor h g))

      (** Leaving us with a square with a functor application. *)

c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit $=> idmap
 exact (fun a => right_unitor a $o braid cat_tensor_unit a).

  Defined.

  (** *** Triangle *)

  (** The triangle identity can easily be proven by rearranging the diagram, cancelling and using naturality of [braid]. *)
  
A: Type
IsGraph0: IsGraph A
Is2Graph0: Is2Graph A
Is01Cat0: Is01Cat A
H: Is1Cat A
H0: HasEquivs A
cat_tensor: A -> A -> A
cat_tensor_unit: A
Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
TriangleIdentity cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit

‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
PentagonIdentity cat_tensor

  
A: Type
IsGraph0: IsGraph A
Is2Graph0: Is2Graph A
Is01Cat0: Is01Cat A
H: Is1Cat A
H0: HasEquivs A
cat_tensor: A -> A -> A
cat_tensor_unit: A
Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d

braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚äóL d ‚àò twist a c b ‚äóL d
‚àò (a ‚äóR braid b c) ‚äóL d ‚àò braid d (a ‚äó (b ‚äó c))
‚àò twist a d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR braid (b ‚äó c) d
‚àò (a ‚äóR braid d (b ‚äó c)
   ‚àò (a ‚äóR twist b d c ‚àò a ‚äóR (b ‚äóR braid c d)))

    
A: Type
IsGraph0: IsGraph A
Is2Graph0: Is2Graph A
Is01Cat0: Is01Cat A
H: Is1Cat A
H0: HasEquivs A
cat_tensor: A -> A -> A
Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò twist (a ‚äó b) d c
‚àò (a ‚äó b) ‚äóR braid c d ‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b ‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚äóL d ‚àò twist a c b ‚äóL d
‚àò (a ‚äóR braid b c) ‚äóL d ‚àò braid d (a ‚äó (b ‚äó c))
‚àò twist a d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR braid (b ‚äó c) d
‚àò a ‚äóR braid d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b d c
‚àò a ‚äóR (b ‚äóR braid c d)

‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò twist (a ‚äó b) d c
‚àò (a ‚äó b) ‚äóR braid c d ‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b ‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d)
‚àò a ‚äóR (b ‚äóR braid d c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist d b c
‚àò twist d a (b ‚äó c) $== braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚äóL d
‚àò twist a c b ‚äóL d ‚àò (a ‚äóR braid b c) ‚äóL d
‚àò braid d (a ‚äó (b ‚äó c))

‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò twist (a ‚äó b) d c
‚àò (a ‚äó b) ‚äóR braid c d ‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b ‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d)
‚àò a ‚äóR (b ‚äóR braid d c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist d b c
‚àò twist d a (b ‚äó c) ‚àò d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid c b) $==
braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚äóL d
‚àò (braid d (c ‚äó (a ‚äó b)) ‚àò d ‚äóR twist a c b)

twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))

(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò

c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c

(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò twist (a ‚äó b) d c
‚àò (a ‚äó b) ‚äóR braid c d ‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò (a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR (b ‚äóR braid d c)) $==
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b)
‚àò d ‚äóR twist a c b ‚àò d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b c)
‚àò twist a d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b d c

c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) d c ‚àò (a ‚äó b) ‚äóR braid c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b) ‚àò 
?Goal $== braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò 
d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚àò 
d ‚äóR twist a c b ‚àò d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b c)
‚àò twist a d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b d c
‚àò a ‚äóR braid (d ‚äó c) b

twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò twist (a ‚äó b) d c
‚àò ((a ‚äó b) ‚äóR braid c d ‚àò (a ‚äó b) ‚äóR braid d c) $==
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b)
‚àò d ‚äóR twist a c b ‚àò d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b c)
‚àò twist a d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b d c
‚àò a ‚äóR braid (d ‚äó c) b ‚àò twist (d ‚äó c) a b
‚àò braid (a ‚äó b) (d ‚äó c)

H0: HasEquivs A
cat_tensor: A -> A -> A
Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b

‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d

braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c) ‚àò twist (a ‚äó b) d c
‚àò braid (d ‚äó c) (a ‚äó b) ‚àò twist a (d ‚äó c) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (d ‚äó c) $== braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c)
‚àò d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚àò d ‚äóR twist a c b
‚àò d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b c) ‚àò twist a d (b ‚äó c)
‚àò a ‚äóR twist b d c

Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor

‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c

‚àò (d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b)

         ‚àò (twist a d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b d c))))

c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c)
‚àò (twist (a ‚äó b) d c
   ‚àò (braid (d ‚äó c) (a ‚äó b)
      ‚àò (twist a (d ‚äó c) b ‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (d ‚äó c)))) $==
braid d ((a ‚äó b) ‚äó c)
‚àò (d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b)
   ‚àò (d ‚äóR twist a c b
      ‚àò (d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b c)
         ‚àò (twist a d (b ‚äó c) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b d c))))

‚àò (braid (d ‚äó c) (a ‚äó b)
   ‚àò (twist a (d ‚äó c) b
      ‚àò (a ‚äóR braid b (d ‚äó c)
         ‚àò (a ‚äóR twist d b c ‚àò twist d a (b ‚äó c))))) $==
d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚àò d ‚äóR twist a c b
‚àò d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b c)

Is01Cat0: Is01Cat A

Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))

(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò

‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
twist (a ‚äó b) d c ‚àò braid (d ‚äó c) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (d ‚äó c) b ‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (d ‚äó c)
‚àò a ‚äóR twist d b c ‚àò twist d a (b ‚äó c) $==
d ‚äóR braid c (a ‚äó b) ‚àò d ‚äóR twist a c b
‚àò d ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b c)

    apply twist_9_gon.

twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c: A
braid b a ‚äóL c ‚àò Œ± b a c ‚àò b ‚äóR braid c a $== Œ± a b c
‚àò braid (b ‚äó c) a ‚àò Œ± b c a

Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c: A
braid b a ‚äóL c ‚àò braid c (b ‚äó a) ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò Id (b ‚äó (c ‚äó a)) $== braid c (a ‚äó b)
‚àò (twist a c b ‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c) ‚àò braid (b ‚äó c) a
‚àò (braid a (b ‚äó c) ‚àò (twist b a c ‚àò b ‚äóR braid c a))

(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c: A
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a ‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $==
twist a c b ‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c

    apply twist_hexagon.
  Defined.

  (** *** Conclusion *)

  (** In conclusion, we have proven the following: *)

  (** There is a monoidal structure on [A]. *)
  Instance ismonoidal_twist
    : IsMonoidal A cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
    := {}.

  (** There is a symmetric monoidal category on [A]. *)
  Instance issymmetricmonoidal_twist
    : IsSymmetricMonoidal A cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
    := {}.

‚àò (c ‚äóR twist a b d ‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d)
   ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d ‚àò twist b a (c ‚äó d)) $==
b
‚äóR (c ‚äóR braid d a
    ‚àò (twist d c a
       ‚àò (d ‚äóR braid a c ‚àò twist a d c
          ‚àò a ‚äóR braid c d)))

    
A: Type
IsGraph0: IsGraph A
Is2Graph0: Is2Graph A
Is01Cat0: Is01Cat A
H: Is1Cat A
H0: HasEquivs A
cat_tensor: A -> A -> A
cat_tensor_unit: A
Is0Bifunctor0: Is0Bifunctor cat_tensor
Is1Bifunctor0: Is1Bifunctor cat_tensor
braid: SymmetricBraiding cat_tensor
twist: forall a b c : A, a ‚äó (b ‚äó c) $-> b ‚äó (a ‚äó c)
twist_twist: forall a b c : A,
twist a b c ‚àò twist b a c $==
Id (b ‚äó (a ‚äó c))
twist_nat: forall (a a' b b' c c' : A) 
(f : a $-> a') (g : b $-> b')
(h : c $-> c'),
twist a' b' c'
‚àò fmap11 cat_tensor f
    (fmap11 cat_tensor g h) $==
fmap11 cat_tensor g
  (fmap11 cat_tensor f h) ‚àò 
twist a b c
right_unitor: RightUnitor cat_tensor cat_tensor_unit
twist_unitor: forall a b : A,
a ‚äóR right_unitor b $== 
braid b a ‚àò b ‚äóR right_unitor a
‚àò twist a b cat_tensor_unit
twist_hexagon: forall a b c : A,
c ‚äóR braid b a ‚àò twist b c a
‚àò b ‚äóR braid a c $== twist a c b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b c ‚àò twist b a c
twist_9_gon: forall a b c d : A,
c ‚äóR braid (a ‚äó b) d ‚àò 
twist (a ‚äó b) c d
‚àò braid (c ‚äó d) (a ‚äó b)
‚àò twist a (c ‚äó d) b
‚àò a ‚äóR braid b (c ‚äó d) $==
c ‚äóR twist a d b ‚àò c ‚äóR (a ‚äóR braid b d)
‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d) ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d
a, b, c, d: A
twist c b (a ‚äó d)
‚àò (c ‚äóR twist a b d ‚àò twist a c (b ‚äó d)
   ‚àò a ‚äóR twist b c d ‚àò twist b a (c ‚äó d)) $==
b ‚äóR (c ‚äóR braid d a)
‚àò b
  ‚äóR (twist d c a
      ‚àò (d ‚äóR braid a c ‚àò twist a d c
         ‚àò a ‚äóR braid c d))
